item.description:
The Remixes (stylized in all-caps) is the first English remix album by TWICE. It was released on November 22, 2023 with "Alcohol-Free (English ver.)" serving as the album's title track.[1]

Track list
  1. "Moonlight Sunrise (Jonas Blue Remix)" - 2:47
  2. "The Feels (Ian Asher Remix)" - 2:51
  3. "Set Me Free (Carneyval Remix)" - 2:57
  4. "Alcohol Free (English ver.)" - 3:30
  5. "Cry For Me (English ver.)" - 3:24
  6. "I Can't Stop Me" (feat. Boys Like Girls) - 3:26
  7. "More & More (Lee Hae Sol Sped Up Remix)" - 2:25
